name: 076 - Contrast | 14"D x 32"H
description: The Contrast Container possesses an organic quality that is anything but shy. A beautifully durable design, this modern planter is constructed from lightweight yet strong fiberglass to resist the elements and wear and tear. Then hand finished to exacting standards in a choice of automotive-grade paints or trademark metal Fusions, an ingenious natural finish that ages gracefully by developing a soft patina over time.
